  "value": "Here's a small sample to demonstrate a few jqPlot features.  The sample that comes with AppStudio shows an example using a date axis.  This one deals with numerical data plotted on three lines with two Y axis.\r\n\r\nThe chart also uses jqPlot's EnhancedLegendRenderer plugin to create a nice legend that is clickable to add or delete plotted lines.\r\n\r\nClick on PlotStuff below to see what it looks like.\r\n\r\nWhen using jqPlot the order of how the library files appear in Project Explorer is critical.  If things aren't in order the app will crash.", 
